{"tid":2342954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"考古學家完整挖掘出龐貝古城快餐食店遺址","createTime":"2020-12-27T13:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T15:23:40.000Z","uid":147376,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eedf1305acf46c4e3b9929b20d86c28c2305d343","tid":2342954,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:53:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=418058&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418058%26refer%3DShare&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=41feb34e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418058%26refer%3DShare&h=8c292fef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=418058&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n考古學家在意大利龐貝古城，挖掘出一間完整的快餐店遺址，店內的畫提供線索，了解當時普羅大眾吃些甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n考古人員至今為止，在龐具古城內發現約八十處快餐店遺跡，但這間是第一間被完整挖掘出土的遺址，考古人員相信是一間出售熱食的店舖。店內有一個L形的櫃枱，挖有多個圓形，用來擺放盛載食物的陶罐。櫃枱前方畫有多幅畫，中間這幅描繪希臘仙女騎馬，跟魚共遊的情景。當時的人吃甚麼呢？<br />\n<br />\n櫃枱前方繪上多幅畫，相信就是店內出售的食物，包括雞和鴨等。考古人員又在店內發現鴨，魚，山羊和蝸牛的骸骨，以及一副完整的狗隻骨骼，還有青銅製的湯勺，盛載液體的雙耳瓶，細頸瓶和一個載油的陶製器皿，現代食肆亦有使用類似的器具。<br />\n<br />\n遺址目前仍未對公眾開放。龐具古城位於意大利那不勒斯東南部約23公里，約有一萬三千人口，公元79年因為火山爆發整座城被火山灰完全掩埋。"},{"pid":"1708a4cc92ec0b2039af9f8f38a181614424d8d4","tid":2342954,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dad0a3538b85f104f9f9e1f10428b98e260a95","tid":2342954,"uid":91771,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:58:01.000Z","msg":"錯重點：做咗咁耐人